        "endTime": 18515,
        "slowStartTime": 25769,
        "slowEndTime": 27998
    },
    {
        "text": "After an hour, she had become good friends with the Haitian teacher,...",
        "startTime": 19086,
        "endTime": 22857,
        "slowStartTime": 28779,
        "slowEndTime": 34511
    },
    {
        "text": "...and this is the magic of children.",
        "startTime": 22960,
        "endTime": 26037,
        "slowStartTime": 34590,
        "slowEndTime": 39280
    },
    {
        "text": "We all have fears.",
        "startTime": 36244,
        "endTime": 37434,
        "slowStartTime": 54516,
        "slowEndTime": 56376
    },
    {
        "text": "Humans are creatures who struggle with the unexpected, unfamiliar and unknown.",
        "startTime": 37923,
        "endTime": 43044,
        "slowStartTime": 57035,
        "slowEndTime": 64791
    },
    {
        "text": "Our human nature does not welcome difference.",
        "startTime": 43565,
        "endTime": 46736,
        "slowStartTime": 65498,
        "slowEndTime": 70329
    },
    {
        "text": "However, I believe we humans can build a society that truly embraces diversity.",
        "startTime": 47025,
        "endTime": 53137,
        "slowStartTime": 70688,
        "slowEndTime": 79930
    },
    {
        "text": "If we can change the unfamiliar to the familiar,...",
        "startTime": 53691,
        "endTime": 56242,
        "slowStartTime": 80687,
        "slowEndTime": 84588
    },
    {
        "text": "...if we can change the courage to seeing differences,...",
        "startTime": 56561,
        "endTime": 60907,
        "slowStartTime": 84991,
        "slowEndTime": 91585
    },
    {
        "text": "...and if we can explore the beauty of diversity,...",
